description:
The Facepower Asset Chain (FAC) is the world's first decentralized chain for community influencers and original creators, aiming to rewrite the Internet's traffic ecosystem through blockchain technology. Transforming the traditional Internet's centralized traffic distribution method into one governed by community users and KOLs (key opinion leader), Facepower redefines the Internet's traffic economy ecosystem.

The FAC project protects the rights of ecosystem participants through smart contracts; transmits and protects the value of information through technologies such as DAI and DID, attracts multiple parties to participate in ecological construction; reduces storage and bandwidth costs through DFS to ensure that information security can be accessed. Official Website：http://facepower.cc
